  <brief_title>Menorrhagia, Dysmenorrhea and Iron Deficiency Among Young Women Soldiers and Effect on Activity</brief_title>
  <official_title>Menorrhagia, Dysmenorrhea and Iron Deficiency Among Young Women Soldiers</official_title>
